    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857717_7_47811-47894",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "47811-47894",
      "markText": "总统蒋介石与副总统李宗仁在就职典礼上，礼服不一致。据说，李宗仁最初被告知总统穿军礼服出席，可临时蒋介石突然改穿中式礼服长袍马褂。正副总统不同调，也象征两人日后的矛盾。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857717&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=47811&rangeEnd=47894",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93832e205d167593849d98c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=47811&rangeEnd=47894"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857717_10_18918-18949",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "18918-18949",
      "markText": "罢免李宗仁的那些“国大代表”，也就是当年高票选举他的同一批人。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857717&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=18918&rangeEnd=18949",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93832e205d167593849d98c?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=18918&rangeEnd=18949"
    },
    {
