      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1369-1438",
      "markText": "那是父亲一段刻骨铭心的回忆，亲身参加武昌起义，对父亲具有重大意义。他见证了中华民国的诞生，由此，对民国始终持有一份牢不可破的“革命感情”。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1369&rangeEnd=1438",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93832e205d167593849d98c?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1369&rangeEnd=1438"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857717_7_59760-59784",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "59760-59784",
      "markText": "父亲与诺兰这张合影，是他在大陆所摄最后一张照片。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857717&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=59760&rangeEnd=59784",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93832e205d167593849d98c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=59760&rangeEnd=59784"
    },
    {
