      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "16385-16446",
      "markText": "在这里，蒋介石把国民党军队最后在东北失败，四十七万精锐尽丧敌手，完全归咎于他自己颁发的那道第二次停战令，这是很严重的说法。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857717&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16385&rangeEnd=16446",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93832e205d167593849d98c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16385&rangeEnd=16446"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857717_3_1658-1689",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1658-1689",
      "markText": "结识李宗仁、黄绍竑，共同从事统一广西的大业，时称“广西三杰”。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1658&rangeEnd=1689",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/93832e205d167593849d98c?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1658&rangeEnd=1689"
    },
    {
